

       Gloom 3 - The Director's Cut is coming....
       ------------------------------------------

   After the success of Gloom 3 "Ultimate Gloom" we at Alpha Software have
   decided to create Gloom 3 - The Directors cut. It will contain :-

   - 80 levels of mayhem including 30 NEW ones!
   - 21 NEW combat levels
   - 2 New zombies and 8 REVAMPED zombies!
   - 49 frames of animation per zombie
   - ALL textures have been REVAMPED including many GREAT NEW ones!
   - 20 Minutes full speech Full Motion Video Intro (030/4meg)
   - Contains the OLD Gloom 3
   - Contains 20 meg of Alpha Software titles and the full website
   - CD only release
   - HALF PRICE to existing Gloom 3 owners!!
   - MANY bug fixes..
   - Brand NEW Guns/menu's/Fonts/Sounds/Gfx/Screens/Scenarios throughout!
   - Numerous versions to work on ALL Amiga Setups with 2 meg Chip even ECS!
   - Even faster c2p routines for more speed..
   - And Much, Much more...

   Suggest improvements YOU want to see in the NEW Gloom 3 Now! eMail me!

